.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThree towers, set within the block structure, rise above the otherwise modest scale of the neighborhood. Their positioning preserves view corridors and open space, while their facades follow the same design language to keep the architectural conversation consistent. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eVlore Beach Urban Development treats the site as a point of convergence, a place where the natural and built environments, the inherited and the emerging are layered.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" alt=\"oppenheim architecture layers village-scale blocks and vibrant towers on albania\u0026#39;s coast\" width=\"818\" height=\"900\" data-src=\"https://static.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/oppenheim-architecture-village-scale-blocks-vibrant-towers-albanian-coast-designboom-08.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://static.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/oppenheim-architecture-village-scale-blocks-vibrant-towers-albanian-coast-designboom-08.jpg 818w, https://static.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/oppenheim-architecture-village-scale-blocks-vibrant-towers-albanian-coast-designboom-08-768x845.jpg 768w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://static.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/oppenheim-architecture-village-scale-blocks-vibrant-towers-albanian-coast-designboom-08.jpg\" srcset=\"https://static.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/oppenheim-architecture-village-scale-blocks-vibrant-towers-albanian-coast-designboom-08.jpg 818w, https://static.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/oppenheim-architecture-village-scale-blocks-vibrant-towers-albanian-coast-designboom-08-768x845.jpg 768w\"/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eOppenheim Architecture introduces a fresh layer to the Vlore’s waterfront fabric\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" alt=\"oppenheim architecture layers village-scale blocks and vibrant towers on albania\u0026#39;s coast\" width=\"818\" height=\"1003\" data-src=\"